snippet.title: Friday the 13th: Amber Heard takes Virginia.
snippet.description:
Rachael and Kevin discuss the latest developments in the Amber Heard Johnny Depp defamation case, specifically her new legal team and the motion for privacy order. 

For more information on this case please check out;
Autumn On Venus on Twitter and YouTube 
@thatbrianFella on Twitter aka Incredibly Average
@sparrabitch on Twitter and her website www.justiceforjohnnydepp.com 


If you like what you see, please like, subscribe and share!
